    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor, age-appropriate surface scratches, and the interior is in great shape with no major tears or stains. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
